"Artificial intelligence" describes several aspirational projects. Current ML techniques constitute "narrow artificial intelligence" useful for making inferences from data. "Artificial general intelligence (AGI)" describes the aspiration of the emulation of human intelligence. "Artificial superintelligence (ASI)" describes the enterprise of exceeding human intelligence. However, there does not exist a consensus on the definition of intelligence, which makes a precise understanding of these comparative definitions difficult.
